       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. MNU001 IS INITIAL.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       REPOSITORY.
        FUNCTION ALL INTRINSIC
        FUNCTION LC5-LDA-IN .
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
        01 CONTEXTO.
            05 USUARIO          PIC X(10).
            05 SESION           PIC X(10).
            05 FILLER           PIC X(205).
        01 LEN                  PIC 9(4) USAGE COMP-5.
        01 LDA                  PIC X(255).
      *  
        01 ARG0                 PIC X(255).
        01 ARG1                 PIC X(255).

       PROCEDURE DIVISION CHAINING ARG0 ARG1.

        CALL "LC5-INIT-PROGRAM" USING 
            BY CONTENT ARG0
            BY CONTENT ARG1
            BY REFERENCE CONTEXTO
        DISPLAY RETURN-CODE

        MOVE LENGTH(ARG0) TO LEN
        CALL "CBL_TOUPPER" USING ARG0 BY VALUE LEN

        DISPLAY ARG0
        DISPLAY ARG1

