        DISPLAY LDA        
        DISPLAY RETURN-CODE        

        MOVE "BAILANDO LAMBADA" TO LDA
        CALL "LC5-LDA-OUT" USING LDA
        DISPLAY RETURN-CODE

        STOP RUN. 

